Hey Blaze!! How's it been?!

I live in Ohio

My first language is English, but i do know some french.

DONUT FILLED CHOCOLATE OBV

Chicken Alfredo is where its at.

My favorite fruit is the old fashion kiwi.

Lemonade

I was looking for a walls server, so i found Avicus. 

When school started, i had alot going on (sports, activities, hw etc..) I couldnt focus on Avicus as much as i did in summer. Now that i have a little bit more freetime, i can be more active. 

I lost my SirCyanide Account and i cant get it back. I choose this name because the word "Cyanide" Sounds cool, and the name "SirCyanide" Sounds cooler imo. But yeah, i really dont like the two "i"s. Maybe a new name could be coming soon.
